data.description:
NO SECURITY DEPOSIT. $300 move-in fee that can be waved if you pay first two months up front. Not currently accepting Section 8. Huge 3 bedroom unit on SECOND FLOOR with IN UNIT WASHER/DRYER, 2 full bathrooms, and garage parking. Master bedroom has ensuite bathroom. 

In-person tours available. Interested applicants should apply right away as the owner is looking to select a tenant soon.

No recent evictions. good credit.

Heat and Water included.
